---
name: draft-bluesky
description: Draft a single post for Bluesky (300 char limit, no hashtags)
triggers:
  - draft a bluesky post
  - write something for bluesky
  - post to bluesky only
  - bluesky post only
---

Read the skill file at `.postlane/commands/draft-bluesky.md`, then draft one post for Bluesky. Output sets `platforms: ["bluesky"]` in `meta.json`.
